text: Mouad Ouites is an Algerian karateka. In 2019, he represented Algeria at the 2019 African Games and he won one of the bronze medals in the men's team kata event. In 2018, he competed in the men's individual kata event at the 2018 World Karate Championships held in Madrid, Spain. In 2019, he also competed at the 2019 African Beach Games held in Sal, Cape Verde where he won the silver medal in the men's individual kata event. He also won the gold medal in the men's team kata event.
